<section
  class="w-full min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center py-16 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-blue-100"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-medium leading-tight mb-6">
      Give your research team
      <span class="text-blue-500">superpowers</span> now
    </h1>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Dataleap is a tailor-made AI assistant for market research. We combine the chatGPT-style interface with a curated
